title: Yenni thalachina Yaedhi adigana
content:
1 - Yenni thalachina Yaedhi adigana

Yenni thalachina Yaedhi adigana
Jarigaethi nee jithamae (2) Prabhuva
Jarigaethi nee jithamae
Nee vaakukai vaechiuhntini
Na pradhana aalakinchuma – Prabhuva
Na pradhana aalakinchuma

Nie thodu layka nee prema layka
Elalona a prani niluvalaydhu (2)
Adavi pugulay nee prema pondhaga (2)
Na pradhana aalakinchuma – Prabhuva
Na pradhana aalakinchuma

Na inti deepam neevaeyanu theylachi
Na rudhayam nee koraku padhila parachuthi (2)
Aari poiyina na vaylugu deepamu (2)
Vayluginchumu nee prematho – prabhuva
Vayluginchumu nee prematho

Ahpadhalu nannu veynnanthiyunna
Naa kaapari neevai nannu ahdhu kontivi (2)
Lokamanthayu nannu vidachina (2)
Nee nundi vaeru chaiyavu – Prabhuva
Nee nundi vaeru chaiyavu

title: Maanava thinamu prabhu swaramalu
content:
2 - Maanava thinamu prabhu swaramalu

Chorus:
Maanava thinamu prabhu swaramalu
Sneygitha sabichudu prabhu premalao

Kaya mulatho nindae thegam
Dhichya manakai manathu ruthiram
Marana mottchanu karathu siluvapai
Thiriki laechanu vijayayudai

Rakshiya naanam thambu thonu
Nithiya suriyuni veluku niithai
Logamantha chattu nenu
Loganathuni siluvaprema

Kirishtu premalo jeeva marungi manthi
Nithya rajyapu mara sulamai
Mahima lona prabhuni kaluva
Siluva paattalo swagatham

title: Erudhayamuna neevuleychi yemi thalachunavy
content:
3 - Erudhayamuna neevuleychi yemi thalachunavy

Erudhayamuna neevuleychi yemi thalachunavy
Nee manasulona yemi thalachi kalavara
Padachuchunavu
Ee dhinamey barama Ee bhrathukey barama

Thoduleyni njeeva yathra
Cheyra leyni kalaithiran
Bhrathikey paruvai povadha
Christhu sthriku svagatham
Cheyru kovanu dhenamu (Erudhamuyani)

Naralavaley yendhalu radha
Kamul neerey thodu kaddha (2)
Ahndha katthi sthuchudan
Jintha aala pradhiyera
Vandha Ialla veedaga

Erudhayamuna nee leychi kalavarapaney
Kalavarapada neylaney
Nee kanla neeru prabhuva chudeehi…

title: Paramuna prabhva varamula naduga
content:
4 - Paramuna prabhva varamula naduga

Paramuna prabhva varamula naduga
Naeveydha kidhi nee, ni padhamulana (2)

Dhana thaanyamulu sarva sampadhalu
Sarva sugamulu ninu kora laydhu
Nee prema nee karuna ne krubhayae chalu
Ninu kaakka naenaedhi marikara laedhu

Elalona na naaithara mughichi
Paralogamunu nay chayruvada
Nay vaela dhutthalu geethalu paada
Nee padha kamalala nanukodhukini poni

title: Sthuthigana mulatho naynu
content:
5 - Sthuthigana mulatho naynu

Sthuthigana mulatho naynu
Na dhevuni sthuthinchadhanu
Na jivithamantha prabhu korakai nay
Nilachivinchadhamu prabhu (sthuthi)

Ahdhi unthamu nivae
Aadhara puthurudu nivae
Prathi jeevini preminchi poshinchu kaatha
Prana neevae
Na premalo ni dhaegalo
Nekuvi neelachanu sthothiramu

Logamantha nee raakakai
Vaychi untini na prabhuva
Mayka vaaka nangu meedha
Motti dhutha ganamulu thoda
Nay vaydhamae ranai unna
Na raja neeku sthothiramu

title: Nithu neethalo nae neelagithi neehirapo
content:
6 - Nithu neethalo nae neelagithi neehirapo

Nithu neethalo nae neelagithi neehirapo
Yeluvalanu jayenulaka
Naduvalanu otarika
Nannu viduvakamu nanu maruvakamu

Neethu nannu nilachunavu
Nee vaniganag nrichunavu
Neevae naathu piranagkakavu
Neevae neethu sharvamu
Neevae na kanamai neerathamu
Neethu magipanu padani
